{"id": 2414, "genre": 1000, "title": "你为什么爱用“佛系/废柴/老年人”之类的词自嘲？", "description": "是为了表达内心的无奈，还是只想跟风自黑一下？（题图来自：视觉中国 © Ikon Images）", "record_count": 12226, "comment_count": 35, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180611180946y2JjtmZFXLxfrsc7.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-06-11T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 4368, "title": "你为什么爱用“佛系/废柴/老年人”之类的词自嘲？", "content": "你觉得大家为什么爱用“佛系/废柴/老年人”之类的词语自嘲？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 286570, "content": "这些词确实可以形容自己，至少某些点戳中了自己内心的焦虑或无力", "image": "img/option/option/20180611182302DhEOxZCclkJPd8A2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 286572, "content": "听上去比“懒”“没出息”好一点，用起来没那么不好意思", "image": "img/option/option/20180611183031b3zwge9rj0iXOpfA.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 286574, "content": "先躺倒自黑一把，别人就不好意思再黑自己了", "image": "img/option/option/20180611183241yYEC8NpTioveFIaK.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 286575, "content": "大家一起自嘲，还能额外获得一种同病相怜的安慰感", "image": "img/option/option/20180611183522jC4uf2bhZnMJq7SW.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 286577, "content": "能体现自己对成功学那套说辞的反抗", "image": "img/option/option/20180611183735L9RntD5UTxihvquP.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 286578, "content": "能借机互相调侃，心理会平衡一些", "image": "img/option/option/20180611183826wXz7kWivplONAKJ0.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 286581, "content": "受到国外流行文化的影响（比如“宅”这个词）", "image": "img/option/option/20180611184146FDq5gXClTbRKeBh4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 286582, "content": "其实没那么丧，只是怕表现得太积极让人觉得不够酷", "image": "img/option/option/201806111847190dtPv1x2bMwC5Xek.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 286583, "content": "没想那么多，看别人都用自己也用了", "image": "img/option/option/20180611185025p2gsirEMbSIkJN4V.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}